description:
Quality Engineering S.R.L. provides manufacturing-focused quality assurance and engineering services. The company supports clients with product and process inspections, dimensional metrology, non-destructive testing, and documentation control. Offerings include supplier qualification and auditing, expediting and vendor surveillance, welding and materials oversight, and conformity assessment support to relevant standards. Teams assist with process capability analysis, root-cause investigation, corrective action planning, and continuous improvement across production lines. Training and technical consulting guide organizations in implementing quality management systems and preparing evidence for third-party certification. || Quality Engineering is an engineering, procurement, and construction company that provides project management and consulting services. | Quality Engineering S.R.L. offers quality assurance, inspection, metrology, NDT, and supplier audits for manufacturing clients. | Quality Engineering S.R.L. provides manufacturing-focused quality assurance and engineering services. The company supports clients with product and process inspections, dimensional metrology, non-destructive testing, and documentation control. Offerings include supplier qualification and auditing, expediting and vendor surveillance, welding and materials oversight, and conformity assessment support to relevant standards. Teams assist with process capability analysis, root-cause investigation, corrective action planning, and continuous improvement across production lines. Training and technical consulting guide organizations in implementing quality management systems and preparing evidence for third-party certification. | Quality Engineering was founded in 1995 as a partnership and in 1998 was established as a limited company. In 2003 it was changed in an engineering company (Inarcassa license n. SI 002613) and from then continuously operates in the following activity areas:
•	process simulation with material and energy balances;
•	process design of chemical industry equipment: heat exchangers, waste heat boilers, steam generators, condensers, columns, reactors, separators, etc.;
•	mechanical design of equipment, pressure vessels calculation (code ASME I, ASME VIII, TEMA, VSR, EN, etc.);
•	piping design (plant layout, 3D-modeling/routing, stress analysis, isometric sketches, etc.);
•	control and instrumentation design (control system architecture, instruments datasheet, control systems, etc.);
•	civil engineering (RC and steel structures design, construction management);
•	procurement for packages and plants (technical specification processing, technical and commercial evaluation of concurrent bidders, supply follow- up/expediting, quality inspection);
•	FEA modeling for thermo-fluid dynamic and structural analysis of chemical industry equipments and its details;
•	energy management of industrial processes, use of energy optimizing, waste heat recovery processes, cogeneration, trigeneration, thermal-solar plants, photovoltaic-solar plants, geothermal heat pumps, power certification of buildings, solutions development for maximizing power efficiency;
•	design and construction management of technological and electric plants for air conditioning in private and industrial sectors; fire-fighting plants; design and balancing of fluid distribution nets; power panels design, functional diagrams, assembling and wiring diagrams;

Castell Bach Engineering Ltd. is an independent multidisciplinary consultancy, with its core services surrounding civil and structural engineering. 

Services include:

Structural steel calculations for homes and commercial properties;
General structural design;
Reinforced concrete foundation design;
Structural and civil engineering specifications;
Drainage philosophies and designs;
Industry standard CAD and design software;
Drawings for planning packs;
Building Regulations support and guidance;
Planning approval support;
Project management;
Construction quality control and inspection test plans;
Construction completions management;
Construction management. || Castell Bach Engineering Ltd. is an independent multidisciplinary consultancy, with its core services surrounding civil and structural engineering. 

